<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Inventory Management</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset some default styles for consistency */
        body, h1, h2, h3, p, ul, li {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Apply basic styling to the page */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: white;
        }

        header {
            background-color: purple;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }

        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

            .about:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            }

            .about h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .about p {
                font-size: 16px;
                color: #555;
            }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            background-color: purple;
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Customize your styles here */
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Inventory Management</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>We are dedicated to providing efficient inventory management solutions for businesses of all sizes. Our goal is to streamline your operations and help you succeed in managing your products, suppliers, and orders.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 I-M-S Product of Group K</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
